doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    title Image Search Abstraction Layer
  body
    h1 Image Search Abstraction Layer
    p This website allows a user to get image URLs, alt text and page urls for a set of images relating to a given search string. The user can also paginate through the responses by adding a ?offset=0 paremeter to the URL. The user can also get a list of most recently submitted search strings.
    h3 To search for 'lolcats funny' with offset 10, use query 'lolcats funny?offset=10':
    p https://image-search-dlzl.herokuapp.com/lolcats funny?offset=10
    h3 To browse recent search queries:
    p https://image-search-dlzl.herokuapp.com/recentsearch
    h3 Credit
    p https://www.freecodecamp.com/challenges/image-search-abstraction-layer
